===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''communication'''  (''plural:'' [[communications]])

# the [[act]] of [[communicating]]
# something [[communicated]]; a [[message]]
# the [[exchange]] or [[transfer]] of [[word]]s, [[thought]]s, [[idea]]s, [[information]] or [[data]] by whatever means
